law.catch_line: Regular interest is payable on member contributions until retirement or withdrawal of accumulated co...
law.text:
Regular interest is payable on member contributions until retirement or withdrawal of accumulated contributions at the rate of:
4% a year, compounded annually, for a member who has transferred from the Employees' Retirement System on or before December 31, 2004; or
5% a year, compounded annually, for each other member.
